    "is_free": false,
    "description": "In the 22nd Century people have settled the near-side of the moon, building massive mining operations for the benefit of Earth, while neglecting the needs of the Lunar people. Tensions with Earth are building, and hit a boiling-point when in 2134 a rogue nation suddenly seizes as much Lunar property as it can with deadly force. As an MI6 agent, you are sent to a mining station taken over by enemy forces in the Hadley-Apennine region. Eliminate the invaders, and frustrate their efforts! You're on your own, so be resourceful. Fight for King and planet!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Lunar Environment</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386790/extras/6e36c26f92f602757d68a22472cf3e7c.avif?t=1699749500\" width=600 height=107 /></span><br>Feel how lunar gravity affects your gameplay. Achieve mad hops, send enemies flying, bounce around in the Lunar Pressurized Vehicle (LPV), or take off with a jetpack!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Weapons</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386790/extras/2d47aa4fdebda71460e32c0adc5a55e2.avif?t=1699749500\" width=600 height=106 /></span><br>Whether you are a gunslinger, heavy gunner, swordsman, or just like blowing things up, you will not be left out. Take on the enemy with a mixed arsenal of weapons that would otherwise weigh you down on Earth!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Freedom of Movement</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386790/extras/3dab66c6b8c21165e039db55cd83e87a.avif?t=1699749500\" width=600 height=106 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Walk or run freely through the experience with smooth VR room-scale locomotion featuring 30 degree snap-turn for comfortable seated gameplay! Smooth player rotation is also supported as an option.<br></li><li>Standing or sitting, the game knows the difference at all times so you do not have to pause the game to change between the two modes.<br></li><li>No need to reach. Lightly hold the grip button and cast a laser to the objects you want to grab, then press fully to teleport them into your hand!</li></ul><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386790/extras/de132ddf80a9ee0425816b4a166c7614.avif?t=1699749500\" width=512 height=512 /></span>",
